        "approach": "Implement the designed solution by running the 'free -h' command via run_shell_command. This will retrieve and display current system memory usage in a clear, formatted manner suitable for monitoring and stability analysis. No file redirection is used; output is streamed directly.",
        "algorithm": "run_shell_command('free -h')",
        "complexity": "O(1)"
